{
  "stem": "13213.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Because many times, they used to come and attack the partisans, to try to wipe out the partisans and attack them.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Attack them from-- attack us from the air.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Many times, we had to move somewhere else.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Would come and bomb the forest.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we lived in such-- in the ground-- such bunkers in the ground, we lived, the whole winter of 1943.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The bunker was built like a V unit like this here, dug inside deep, and then covered with all kind of branches-- big branches-- and covered with earth-- leaves and earth.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then we had a stove inside.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Built a very primitive stove, and it was very nice and warm.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We made such banks and we slept on the banks.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I remember singing with them, and I had a good voice.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I used to sing for-- with them and life was very good for us.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, in our unit, the Diadia Petia was 2,000.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Fedorov had about 4,000 people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well-- well, you're talking about forests.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Big, big.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Not hiding, really fighting.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] We didn't have to hide because it was just like a military unit.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Used to attack the German-- the Germans at the railroad crossings and all kind of special assignments the partisans were getting from Moscow.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, later on we were getting, actually, parachute-- parachuters coming in from Moscow, flying in and dropping ammunition and some armaments.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And also, what they took away from the Germans.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Attacking the Germans, they took away a lot of arms.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I wouldn't say that I saw, but I did use a gun for a while.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But not knowingly, no.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This went on for almost, yeah, a year, until 1944.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were close by with the units.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
